content: 有个轿夫不会说客套话，有一次，他和另外几个轿夫把一位秀才抬上山后，轿夫问道：“相公，‘令尊’是什么意思？”秀才捉弄他说：“这‘令尊’二字字么，是称呼人家儿子的。”说完偷偷地掩嘴而笑。
content_en: One of the bearers didn't say anything. Once he and a few other bearers lifted a scholar to the hill, the bearer asked, 'What does it mean to be a respector?' The scholar teased him. ' This word Zun Zun means to call people's sons. Then secretly cover his mouth and laugh.
